metadata.name: Octopus 0001
metadata.description:
This token represents your ownership of membership to our private yacht club at the power tier.
As a Fathom Yacht Club member, you will have access to our private member events, yacht charters, voting, and travel partners.
As a member, you choose the yacht size between 35-50' youâ€™d like for your reservation and are entitled to bring guests (non-token holders) based on yacht capacity.
All charter costs are not included in the token price.  
This token is also a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.
